						<p>On a slab in a field to the south of the village.</p>						

						<p>Registers the grant of land by Kāṭama-Reḍḍi Aki-Reḍḍi, the servant of Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Birudurgamarāju and the Raḍḍis of Bairēpalli to the god Kūḍali Rāmēśvaradēva.</p>						

